g-count:
* '''$1''' is a user name
* '''$2''' is his or her count of gifts
g-created-by:
Complete contents of a cell in a table. The next cell (horizontally) contains the user name of the creator of a gift. {{gender}}

gift_received_body:
* $1 is a the (real) user name

* $5 is a link to the user preferences
